@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title 控制权状态机

state "Observer" as Observer <<Neutral>>
state "PendingGrant" as PendingGrant <<Transit>>
state "Controller" as Controller <<ActiveState>>
state "Preempting" as Preempting <<Transit>>
state "Released" as Released <<Terminal>>
state "Revoked" as Revoked <<Risk>>
state "Rejected" as Rejected <<Risk>>

[*] --> Observer

Observer --> PendingGrant : AuthorityRequest(action=Claim)
PendingGrant --> Controller : AuthorityStatus(state=Controller)
PendingGrant --> Rejected : AuthorityStatus(state=Rejected)
Rejected --> Observer : 观察方保留会话

Controller --> Controller : Renew / lease_ttl_ms 更新
Controller --> Preempting : AuthorityRequest(action=Preempt)
Preempting --> Controller : 抢占成功并保留当前租约
Preempting --> Revoked : 被更高优先级会话抢占

Controller --> Released : AuthorityRequest(action=Release)
Controller --> Revoked : Lease Expired\n或 route 失效
Released --> Observer : 租约主动归还
Revoked --> Observer : 租约失效后回到观察态

note right of PendingGrant
主路径关心三件事：
- 谁申请控制权
- 是否进入 Controller
- 若失败，是否给出拒绝原因
end note

note bottom of Preempting
Preempting 是分支态：
它表达的是控制权竞争，
不是新的稳定控制态。
end note
@enduml
